Need an explanation. <Selection Dialog>What is Fish Ranking. Explain the rules. How to register. Viewing results. Awards. No, thanks.<Prompt>
Fish Ranking is a contest held periodically by the Fishermen's Guild. Participants compete based on a set of defined rules regarding the size and weight of a certain big fish.<Prompt>

To participate, you must acquire the fish we specified for the contest and bring it here. We won't look over your shoulder to see if you're catching your fish or buying them. That's your personal decision.<Prompt>
You can only have one fish entered for Fish Ranking at once. You can choose to overwrite your current entry with a new catch, but you won't be able to re-register your previous submission.<Prompt>
We will announce the results after the submission period ends. The top ten entries will receive a modest award and prize money, as well as a new title.<Prompt>
Fish are judged based on a set of predetermined rules.<Prompt>
The rules are simple. All fish are inscribed with their size (Im) and weight (Pz). The contest may be judged based on either number, or even both values added together.<Prompt>
Depending on the rules, the person who caught the fish with the lowest or the greatest value wins!<Prompt>

Value is determined by the calculation of  points  and evaluated based on the contest rules. For example, when the rules designate the  smallest fish,  the person with the fewest points will win.<Prompt>
During the submission period, I will inform everyone what criterion we are judging by, so just ask if you're curious!<Prompt>
If you would like to submit an entry, please <Set colour #5>trade<Set colour #1> the fish specified for the contest to me, and I will give it a rough inspection.<Prompt>

The fish will be registered if I deem it is suitable for the contest. You may only have one fish registered at a time. Registering a second specimen will remove your previous submission from the entry database.<Prompt>
After you pay the registration fee, I will return your fish to you. All that's left afterwards is to wait for the results.<Prompt>
To ensure a fair contest, we will label your fish before returning it.<Prompt>
This will not affect the fish other than disqualifying it from reentry in Fish Ranking. You can still cook the fish, sell it at auction, or use it for quests.<Prompt>
After the submission period ends, the results will be announced. To view the ranking board, just speak to me.<Prompt>
Anybody may view the ranking board. You'll especially want to check if you or a friend participated in the last contest. Perhaps one of you will be listed on the board, too!<Prompt>
The top ten contestants will receive a modest award consisting of prize money from the Fishermen's Guild and a new title.<Prompt>
In addition, participants in the top twenty will receive <Possible Special Code: 01> <Singular/Plural Choice (Parameter 1)><Singular/Plural Choice (Parameter 5)>$   as a souvenir.<Prompt>
You may only receive your award while the results are being announced, so be sure that you are here on time!<Prompt>

Hello, faithful fans! Mighty Maiden Uka here
!Just by looking at your smiling faces, I can tell you're all having a great time at this year's Sunbreeze Festival! So, are you rrready for some music. I know we're ready to sing our hearrrts out
!...Um, or at least I am. Where in sweet Selbina could Mumor be!
.Oh well, the show must go on. It's a little embarrassing to sing by myself, but any entertainer worth her miraclesalt would jump at this opporrrtunity. This is my chance to go solo
!Everyone, feast your earrrs upon my astounding aria

Your cacophonous warbling is enough to make me vacate the contents of my stomach. These people are not stupid, either... They know that without your partner, you aren't even worth the stage on which you stand
Who goes there!
.Who, indeed... Understandable, since I believe this is the first time I've deigned to grace you with my presence. I am a diva. Does that appellation ring any bells for you, pray tell
.A diva!. They truly exist!
.Oh, so you have indeed heard of my kind. No wonder you were once my master's favorite archfiend
Though, in all truth, the title  archfiend  refers to nothing more than washed-up hacks who possess neither the drive nor the talent to reach for the stars...of divadom
!Yet now you've thrown even that away, settling for a mundane life of belching out dull drivel at vulgar venues. Someone as wretched as you holds no value whatsoever
Or do you.... I heard you associate with some upstart floozy who dares defy my master and dissuades archfiends from our cause. Do you know where she is
.Well, it seems you're all alone. No matter. She'll simply have to wait until I'm finished with you
Cooome now, my preeecious!.
.Of course, someone of my sublime stature would never condescend to personally dispatch with a peon like you. This minion should prove more than a sufficient substitute for accomplishing that task

The crowd here may be raucous, but drown out its pesky din.  Now give yourself up to your dreams, just cast away your strife.  Next, let your heavy eyelids fall and drool drip down your chin.  This soothing, tranquil lullaby leaves all bereft of life..
.Even without Mumor...I can cut this cocky diva down to size! Everyone, lend me your strength
!Yeep
!Hmph, it seems you may possess at least an iota of skill after all
I'm not alone. I have the whole audience on my side! Let's do this, everyone
!Neo Crrrystal Jig!!
!Super Crrrusher Jig!!
!Shining Summerrr Samba!!
!Lovely Mirrracle Waltz!!
!Grrr...
!Don't just stand there and take it, you invariably incompetent imbecile
!Neo Crystal Jig
!Super Crusher Jig
!Shining Summer Samba
!Lovely Miracle Waltz
!Urk...

We must all work as one! Please, lend me your strrrength

Ahahaha! Those earth tones truly do bring your outfit together, Uka
You archfiends exist as nothing more than mere stepping stones on my path to glory! It matters not how many enemies assail me. I can dispatch them all with but the bat of an eye
!You may now exit stage right. Oh, and I don't think you'll need to worry about any encores
Fear not, I'll be sure to invite your friend to the after-party as well
!Ahhhhhh!!
!Bwahahaha!!
!And so, without Mumor, Uka quickly succumbed to the diva and was banished to an interdimensional purgatory..
Be more supportive of her and you can overturn what has just transpired. Band together and cheer on Uka to save her from the diabolical diva
!Haaah, haaah... I've got to hand it to you. I don't think I can beat you by myself. If only Mumor were herrre, too
Mumor. Oh, you mean that sorry excuse for a nemesis
Just how might the addition of one more classless poseur change what is so obviously inevitable
.You certainly are persistent. My master must have seen... But enough chatter! This time I shall truly send you off into eternal slumber with a special lullaby
In the name of joy and happiness, I shall punish you
!Mumor

!A what with whom

.Huh. Oh, yeah. She's a diva--one of Ullegore's songstrrresses--which means she has a much more talented voice than any of us forrrmer archfiends
Another one. I'm sick and tired of Ullegore's lackeys trying to ruin our performances
!Ruin. Your act doesn't leave much to ruin. Besides, this stage was built for a diva of my caliber, not amateurs such as yourselves
H-how dare you! My sultry singing is the perfect complement to Uka's dynamic dancing, and that's why our popularity soars higher than any airship
!Think what you will. We shall see if you're still singing the same tune after I show you how to hold a true note
This is simply impossible! How can the addition of one saucy starlet change the tide of battle so
.I guess you haven't heard
Mumor can absorrrb the energy from her cheerrring fans to unleash a devastating attack..

Our power levels climb to over nine thousand!!
!P-power levels!. What sort of nonsense are you-
-Let's play off this hoary old has-been before she even has a chance to butcher her swan song
!To see the inverted rainbow of your smile..
We'll dance to the abyss and back
!Mighty Maidens Mumor and Uka
!Eternal Vana Illusion!!

Ullegore!

Not so fast

Atmacite is best described as the crystalline agglomeration of a creature's soul. Our scientists have succeeded in discovering a way to tap its power to serve the efforts of the Voidwatch.<Prompt>
By infusing one's body with atmacite, it is possible to obtain powers akin to those once possessed by the creature whence it came, rather like turning a beast's fangs upon its own kind.<Prompt>

At first glance, atmacite appears to be the perfect artificial enhancement. However, it does suffer from a single limitation: its power is unleashed only when engaged in a Voidwatch operation.<Prompt>
Research to identify the exact reason for this continues, but most scientists find the spectral alignment theory compelling.<Prompt>
That is, being formed of Voidwalker souls, atmacite will surge to life only when its bearer is existentially aligned to its dimension of origin.<Prompt>
From this it can be inferred that Voidwalkers are stripped of considerable strength when they cross over into Vana'diel.<Prompt>
But I suspect this is of little interest to a layman like you. Allow me to return to the subject at hand.<Prompt>
The infusion of atmacite requires cruor, a potent energy source that takes the form of shiny red granules.<Prompt>
Cruor is obtainable by various means, felling a Voidwalker being the most common of all. As you can never have too much cruor, I urge you to be diligent in its procurement.<Prompt>
We've recently perfected a method for improving atmacite potency. The process is called enrichment, and involves fusing cruor on to atmacite to amplify its power.<Prompt>

Atmacite can be enriched in stages up to a maximum of level <Numeric (Parameter 0)>. The quantity of cruor required varies with the variety of atmacite as well as its current enrichment level.<Prompt>

Under normal conditions, atmacite enrichment is an intensive process that demands trained hands. For reasons yet to be determined, however, both infusion and enrichment can be safely performed by laymen, provided they're at a planar rift.<Prompt>
Keep this in mind should the need arise to reconfigure your atmacite with haste.<Prompt>
